videos.headline: Lucky Bounce for Georgia
videos.description: The ball bounces off of the hands of Terry Godwin, the intended receiver, but teammate Jeb Blazevich ends up with the completion against Ole Miss.

videos.headline: Ole Miss strikes with pick six
videos.description: Jacob Eason pass intercepted for a TD Derrick Jones return for 53 yds for a TD

videos.headline: Ole Miss extends early lead
videos.description: D'Vaughn Pennamon run for 1 yd for a TD

videos.headline: Ole Miss QB scrambles and finds WR in double coverage for 55-yard TD
videos.description: Ole Miss QB Chad Kelly scrambles out of the pocket, avoids a tackle and then launches a 55-yard touchdown pass to DaMarkus Lodge to extend the Rebels' lead against Georgia.

videos.headline: Georgia looks to shift momentum with fake punt
videos.description: Marshall Long pass complete to Sony Michel for 28 yds to the Miss 32 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Georgia RB Chubb leaves game with ankle injury
videos.description: Georgia RB Nick Chubb leaves game with an ankle injury in the second quarter against Ole Miss and would not return.

videos.headline: Ole Miss continues to rout Georgia with 9-yard TD
videos.description: Rebels QB Chad Kelly finds Evan Engram, who jumps way up and grabs a 9-yard pass for a touchdown against the Bulldogs.

videos.headline: Ole Miss continues dominance with second half opening drive score
videos.description: Jason Pellerin pass complete to Eugene Brazley for 5 yds for a TD

videos.headline: Chad Kelly takes it 41 yards to the house
videos.description: Ole Miss QB Chad Kelly fakes the handoff before running 41 yards untouched for the touchdown, extending the Rebels' lead to 44-0.

videos.headline: Georgia gets on the board late in third quarter
videos.description: Brian Herrien run for 10 yds for a TD
